{
  "id": 2892,
  "name": "Kadim Yapı: İtici",
  "desc": "<p>The guardians of the lost ancient desert ruins have power enough to punish any who would presume to disturb the pure dreams of their lord.</p><p>These machines were not first built to be temple guards or palace defenders, but instead to rebirth the paradise that the foolish desert ruler dreamed of. </p><p>Today, that utopia is long gone, and the dreams and oaths, forgotten by the world, are now only found in the mantras inscribed upon these machines.</p>",
  "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/07/1023623/60aa5a703106abea12e09b790da7972b_6856390141898102128.png",
